China's entry into the World Trade Organization, U.S. officials
said Tuesday that ``difficult and complex issues remain across all
areas of trade.'' By Erik Eckholm.
</P>
<P>
   HONGKONG-IMMIG (Hong Kong) _ In a decision that reflects rising
fears about a flood of immigrants from mainland China, a Hong Kong
court today ruled against 17 mainland residents who had claimed the
right to live here. By Mark Landler.
</P>
