the status of solvency of Social Security and Medicare. By David E.
Rosenbaum.
</P>
<P>
   SCOTUS-VENUE (Washington) _ A crime spree may be prosecuted in
any of the locations of the crimes, the Supreme Court rules. By
Linda Greenhouse.
</P>
<P>
   AIRLINES-DISABLED (Washington) _ Disabled air travelers are
frequently mistreated by airline personnel and denied special
accommodations including access to wheelchairs and escorts in
violation of a 1986 law, according to the National Council on
Disability.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; NATIONAL GENERAL &LR;  (``a'' code)
</P>
<P>
   FLA-RETARDED (Miami) _ A state investigation has concluded that
administrators for one of South Florida's largest not-for-profit
social service agencies siphoned off tax dollars to boost their
salaries while neglecting care for their mentally retarded clients.
</P>
