</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-MATRIX-FILM-LADN </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
WACHOWSKIS TAKE QUANTUM LEAP WITH NEW ACTION FILM
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By BOB STRAUSS 
c.1999 Los Angeles Daily News  
<TEXT>
