<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-03-30 17:03 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A9772 &Cx1f; tad-z
u w &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-KOSOVO-BOSNIA-0331-CO     03-30 0763
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-KOSOVO-BOSNIA-0331-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    LETTER FROM SARAJEVO: A RAVAGED LAND PLEADS DON'T LET IT HAPPEN
