speech to take account of the war in Kosovo, Russian President
Boris N. Yeltsin told political leaders today that Russia ``will
not allow itself to be drawn into military conflict.'' By Celestine
Bohlen.
</P>
<P>
   KOSOVO-ISRAEL (Jerusalem) _ Benjamin Netanyahu, the Israeli
