<P>
   KOSOVO-NATO (Brussels, Belgium) _ Its carefully laid bombing
plans still unsuccessful in forcing Yugoslav President Slobodan
Milosevic to stop his attacks against ethnic Albanian civilians in
Kosovo, the NATO alliance wrestles with the question, what next? By
Craig R. Whitney.
