</P>
<P>
   TAURUS-DESIGN (New York) _ Ford unveiled the new Taurus on
Tuesday at the New York International Auto Show. It is unlikely to
win any contests for style. Indeed, the most distinctive thing
about it is probably how indistinguishable it is from all the other
look-alike midsize sedans. By Keith Bradsher.
</P>
<P>
   (ART ADV: Photo and graphic are being sent to NYT photo/graphic
