to reveal what caused the crash last Saturday of a $45 million
F-117A stealth aircraft over Yugoslavia. But despite criticism, it
may never give the details. Officials say they don't want to admit
that a plane once believed to be virtually invisible to radar may
be vulnerable. By ERIC ROSENBERG. (Already filed.)
